title: Trailer for Doing Justice
description:
Doing Justice, a new podcast based on Preet’s book of the same name, debuts Wednesday, January 27th. You can listen for free by searching “Doing Justice” on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, or the podcast player of your choice. Here’s the direct link to the podcast on Apple Podcasts: apple.co/doingjustice And here’s the direct link to the podcast on Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/show/3MZrn7Qz9BpqtMXaPi8Hst?si=V3IsXds8Sc-efDlnb3iBXQ See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
Learn more about your ad choices. Visit podcastchoices.com/adchoices
